# Copy to `.dev.vars` (gitignored) for local `wrangler dev`.
#
# AMT_ENDPOINT wires the worker to a local Aria-AMT transcription server so live
# practice chunks produce performance MIDI and the tier-1 score-relative grounding
# path runs (per-bar onset/duration deviations vs the notated score, #64). Start
# the server with `just amt` (listens on port 8001). Without this, AMT calls fail
# and sessions degrade to Tier 3 (scores only). Production keeps AMT_ENDPOINT=""
# in wrangler.toml until a deliberate deploy.
AMT_ENDPOINT="http://localhost:8001"
